    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bonnie_bassler_547880",
        "quote": "We've all been sick; we're all afraid of infection. I think the easiest application to help people understand what quorum sensing is and why it's important to study is to tell them that if we could make the bacteria either deaf or mute, we could create new antibiotics.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bonnie Bassler",
            "url": "/quotes/bonnie_bassler_547880"
