            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bonnie_bassler_694073",
        "quote": "Think about all kinds of infectious diseases, like mumps or measles or chicken pox. When a virgin population encountered those pathogens, it ravaged the population, and now they're childhood diseases, and eventually they won't even be that. That's our relationship with bacteria, going through time.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bonnie Bassler",
            "url": "/quotes/bonnie_bassler_694073"
