                "url": "/topics/infectious"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bonnie_bassler_694079",
        "quote": "If a bacterium is trying to infect you, it won't secrete alone, because your immune system will block it. Bacteria will hide until they can all act together and make an impact.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bonnie Bassler",
            "url": "/quotes/bonnie_bassler_694079"
        },
