                "name": "Riddles",
                "url": "/topics/riddles"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bonnie_bassler_694075",
        "quote": "I realized that lab research was the perfect path for me. It allowed me to spend every day figuring out mysteries/puzzles that have to do with what make us alive. What could be a bigger mystery or puzzle?",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bonnie Bassler",
            "url": "/quotes/bonnie_bassler_694075"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Perfect",
